<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Onboarding Letter - {{companyName}}</title>
    <!-- Use a sophisticated serif font to match the reference document -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 0;
        }
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
            font-size: 11px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .a4-container {
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            position: relative;
            background: white;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        /* Top Banner Section */
        .top-banner {
            width: 100%;
            padding-top: 25mm;
            padding-bottom: 5mm;
            padding-left: 20mm;
            padding-right: 20mm;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .banner-content {
            width: 100%;
            height: 45mm;
            background-color: #1b263b; /* Dark Blue */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: stretch;
        }

        .banner-text-wrapper {
            padding: 10mm 15mm;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .banner-title {
            color: #e5e1d8; /* Cream color for text */
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .banner-title-italic {
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .logo-box {
            background-color: #2d5a27; /* Dark Green */
            width: 45mm;
            padding: 8mm 5mm;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .company-name-vertical {
            color: #e5e1d8;
            font-size: 15px;
            text-align: right;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            white-space: pre-line;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
        }

        /* Main Body Layer */
        .content-layer {
            flex-grow: 1;
            padding: 10mm 25mm 20mm 25mm;
        }

        /* Salutation */
        .salutation {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #1b263b;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        /* Intro text */
        .body-text {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .body-text p {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        /* Info Sections (restyled for this template) */
        .info-block {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1b263b;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e1d8;
            padding-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .details-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px 40px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            width: calc(50% - 20px);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }

        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            width: 100px;
            color: #1b263b;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Checklists */
        .checklist {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            columns: 2;
        }
        .checklist li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            break-inside: avoid-column;
        }
        .checklist li:before {
            content: "•";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #2d5a27;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Schedule Table */
        .schedule-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .schedule-table th {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 6px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #1b263b;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1b263b;
        }
        .schedule-table td {
            padding: 6px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e1d8;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Signature Area */
        .signature-block {
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15mm;
        }
        .closure-text {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }
        .sender-name {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1b263b;
        }
        .sender-title {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #4a5568;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* Footer Bar */
        .footer-bar-container {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0 15mm 15mm 15mm;
            display: flex;
        }

        .footer-bar-content {
            width: 100%;
            height: 25mm;
            display: flex;
            align-items: stretch;
        }

        .footer-segment-blue {
            background-color: #1b263b; /* Dark Blue */
            flex-grow: 2.5;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 15mm;
        }

        .footer-segment-green {
            background-color: #2d5a27; /* Dark Green */
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .footer-segment-cream {
            background-color: #e5e1d8; /* Cream */
            width: 20mm;
        }

        .footer-meta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; /* Keep meta info sans-serif for readability */
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .footer-meta-block {
            display: flex;
            border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            padding-left: 10px;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="a4-container">
        <!-- Top Banner -->
        <div class="top-banner">
            <div class="banner-content">
                <div class="banner-text-wrapper">
                    <h1 class="banner-title"><span class="banner-title-italic">Welcome</span> to<br>the team</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="logo-box">
                    <div class="company-name-vertical">{{#if companyName}}{{companyName}}{{else}}SITWELL<br>FINANCIAL{{/if}}</div>
                    <!-- Diamond SVG Logo -->
                    <svg class="logo-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M12 2L2 12L12 22L22 12L12 2Z" stroke="#e5e1d8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                        <path d="M12 5.5L5.5 12L12 18.5L18.5 12L12 5.5Z" stroke="#e5e1d8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                        <path d="M2 12H22" stroke="#e5e1d8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                        <path d="M12 2V22" stroke="#e5e1d8" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-layer">
            <div class="salutation">
                Dear {{employeeName}},
            </div>

            <div class="body-text">
                <p>Welcome to <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>! We are excited to have you on board and look forward to the contributions you will make as <strong>{{position}}</strong> in our <strong>{{department}}</strong> department.</p>
                <p>As a new member of our team, you will be joining a group of talented and dedicated individuals who are committed to excellence. We believe in fostering a positive and collaborative work environment where everyone can grow and succeed together.</p>
                <p>We understand that starting a new job can be overwhelming, so please know that we are here to support you every step of the way. Your official start date is <strong>{{startDate}}</strong>.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-block">
                <div class="section-title">First Day Details</div>
                <div class="details-grid">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Reporting Time:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{#if startTime}}{{startTime}}{{else}}9:00 AM{{/if}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Location:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{#if workLocation}}{{workLocation}}{{else}}Main Office{{/if}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Contact Person:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{#if hrContactPerson}}{{hrContactPerson}}{{else}}HR Desk{{/if}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-label">Dress Code:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">{{#if dressCode}}{{dressCode}}{{else}}Business Casual{{/if}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-block">
                <div class="section-title">What to Bring</div>
                <ul class="checklist">
                    <li>Valid Photo ID</li>
                    <li>Bank Account Details</li>
                    <li>Educational Certificates</li>
                    <li>Previous Relieving Letter</li>
                    <li>Passport Photos (4)</li>
                    <li>Signed Offer Letter</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-block">
                <div class="section-title">First Week Schedule</div>
                <table class="schedule-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th style="width: 25%;">Day</th>
                            <th style="width: 75%;">Activity</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Day 1</strong></td>
                            <td>Welcome session, IT setup, and HR documentation.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Day 2</strong></td>
                            <td>Company orientation and departmental introductions.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>Day 3-5</strong></td>
                            <td>Role-specific training and initial project syncs.</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>

            <div class="body-text" style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <p>If you have any questions or concerns before your start date, please don't hesitate to reach out to your colleagues or me.</p>
                <p>Once again, welcome to the team! We are thrilled to have you with us and can't wait to see what we will achieve together.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="signature-block">
                <div class="closure-text">Best regards,</div>
                <div class="sender-name">{{#if hrContactPerson}}{{hrContactPerson}}{{else}}Human Resources Manager{{/if}}</div>
                <div class="sender-title">{{#if hrPhone}}Contact: {{hrPhone}}{{/if}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer Bar -->
        <div class="footer-bar-container">
            <div class="footer-bar-content">
                <div class="footer-segment-blue">
                    <div class="footer-meta">
                        <div class="footer-meta-block">
                            <span>{{companyName}}</span>
                            <span>{{companyAddress}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="footer-meta-block">
                            <span>{{#if hrEmail}}{{hrEmail}}{{else}}{{companyEmail}}{{/if}}</span>
                            <span>{{#if hrPhone}}{{hrPhone}}{{else}}{{companyPhone}}{{/if}}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-segment-green"></div>
                <div class="footer-segment-cream"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
 </div>
</body>
</html>